## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **sotorasib Lumakras 2021** = first KRAS G12C inhibitor — 4 decades 의 "undruggable KRAS" 종료. switch-II pocket + covalent C12 cysteine targeting. quantum-VQE 의 covalent allosteric scaffold 가 직접 fit. CodeBreak100 OS modest (~12.5m vs docetaxel) — 후속 generation 필요.
2. **adagrasib Krazati 2022** = second KRAS G12C — CNS penetration 우월 (brain met). KRYSTAL-1 OS ~14m. sotorasib + adagrasib 후 broader pan-KRAS (G12D + G12V + Q61H) 가 next quantum-VQE target.
3. **osimertinib Tagrisso 2015 → 1L 2018 → adjuvant ADAURA 2020** = EGFR T790M 3rd gen → 1L → adjuvant 의 sequential indication expansion paradigm. C797S resistance 가 4th gen + ASO + bispecific 의 다음 frontier.
4. **amivantamab + lazertinib (한미 Leclaza) 2024 1L global** = 한국 first 1L EGFR global (MARIPOSA). EGFR + MET bispecific + 3rd gen TKI combo > osimertinib 단독 (PFS+). cross-K_pharma_industry 의 first global 1L lung cancer.
5. **trastuzumab deruxtecan (Enhertu) 2024 HER2-mut NSCLC expansion** = ADC paradigm 의 lung cancer entry. DESTINY-Lung01/02 ORR 대폭 (HER2-mut). HER3 (patritumab-DXd) + TROP2 (dato-DXd) 가 next ADC wave.
6. **tarlatamab Imdelltra 2024 first DLL3xCD3 BiTE — R/R SCLC** = SCLC 의 첫 targeted therapy (4 decade chemo paradigm 종료). DeLLphi-301 ORR 40% R/R. quantum-VQE 의 BiTE scaffold + DLL3 epitope 가 직접 fit.
7. **alectinib + lorlatinib ALK 2nd → 3rd gen** = ALK CNS penetration 우월 + 1L ALEX trial alectinib > crizotinib. lorlatinib CROWN 5y PFS landmark.
8. **selpercatinib + pralsetinib RET 2020** = RET fusion NSCLC + medullary thyroid (cross-endocrine) — tissue-agnostic precedent.
9. **PACIFIC durvalumab consolidation Stage III 2018** = unresectable Stage III post-CRT consolidation IO paradigm. KEYNOTE-189/407 + IMpower150 + CheckMate 9LA 가 1L 변화. 1L NSCLC PD-L1 high → IO 단독 (pembrolizumab) + PD-L1 low → IO+chemo combo.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, lung-cancer-specific 임상 의미 한정.

